title: Here’s an Exclusive Look Inside Nike’s NYFW Event in NYC
text:
Visit the original post to see all 11 images from this gallery. 
During New York Fashion Week: Men’s , Nike took the opportunity to showcase a number of new products , namely a series of high profile collaborations. If you weren’t able to make it out, or simply need a refresher on what went down, we’ve got you covered via a set of exclusive imagery.
The above gallery in turn provides a glimpse at the ACRONYM x NikeLab Air Force 1 Downtown , VLONE Air Force 1 , as well as some of the major players behind the projects, in addition to those in attendance. You will also see hints of Nike’s joint efforts with Riccardo Tisci and COMME des COMME des GARÇONS .
Click through the photos above to check it all out.
